de.esoco.ewt.event

Enum EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventType>
      • de.esoco.ewt.event.EventType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EventType>

    public enum EventType
extends java.lang.Enum<EventType>
    An enumeration of all GEWT event types for which event listeners can be registered on components. Focus and pointer events are supported by all components. Which other event types are supported can be found out from the documentation of the respective component.
